      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. Balancing innovation vs safety is tough. But realistically, if we're talking about actual extinction-level events, isn't the \"innovation\" argument a bit of a distraction? Like, isn't it objectively better to be safe than to risk everything just to stay ahead in a race?",
